{"tid":175661,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇音樂/考級 巴/絲入來吹下水","createTime":"2017-03-27T15:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T06:20:34.000Z","uid":14715,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0df42010bbf135895c6fc943aae70a13b4e2c96b","tid":175661,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"音樂台太多小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先利申：玩左7年音樂，而家兼職教打鼓， 食緊穀種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家搵緊份本科全職， 希望in 得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過多兩個月考豎琴8級， d歌好難。 同埋學琴超貴， 唯有自修8級既歌再搵老師執..<br />\n<br />\n自己一路堅持住玩音樂， 一路處理自己情緒病， 都叫捱過左好多年. 但有時真係要向現實低頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇音樂巴絲講下生活點？<br />\n<br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df008d672b0c563ab61f71424ca75441bdcadc0","tid":175661,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T17:12:30.000Z","msg":"我唔係玩音樂嘅人 但想你繼續堅持<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05fb2dfadd8f2853c7760c82e5d2aaab74cc5cb","tid":175661,"uid":42202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"8級Percussion <br />\n教左4-5年小學中學既興趣班考試班樂團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊學邊教邊做<br />\n好鐘意見到學生由0去到100"},{"pid":"948bdf32696626cc9cd8649c35ecfe03445d7fb7","tid":175661,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8級Percussion <br />\n教左4-5年小學中學既興趣班考試班樂團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊學邊教邊做<br />\n好鐘意見到學生由0去到100</blockquote><br />\n巴打全職教？ 搵唔搵到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"ff361febb25cead2cea3a859f9e974b23e3faf11","tid":175661,"uid":56837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:57:07.000Z","msg":"考到演奏級作用都不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係揸兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b55502def01ad5d8e5bbf13037a275cac64039","tid":175661,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考到演奏級作用都不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係揸兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我真係諗住搬部琴出街玩， 等人掉錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者等人執我返去比show 我出"},{"pid":"cf5e5202ab693be364dc9106eb47a302c7183f21","tid":175661,"uid":38765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩music degree grad左<br />\n全職教琴路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做得呢行真係要慢慢儲學生<br />\n要捱得可能隔一個鐘先有一個學生嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f715e4a3081c0e428fd842ea510271245aad94f","tid":175661,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:34:16.000Z","msg":"玩古琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44142921d5d31b0a96b7606331b1f485cc7d0b6a","tid":175661,"uid":73406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:37:57.000Z","msg":"學咗十幾年先考八級(當時22歲)，想問一問考唔考演奏級好?只係為興趣，問一問。<br />\n八級只係攞merit，唔高&hellip;重要考試個阿sir比分鬆手先得&hellip;"},{"pid":"721d3dc54d9229a4b396fc18a409ba60db0d4f80","tid":175661,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學咗十幾年先考八級(當時22歲)，想問一問考唔考演奏級好?只係為興趣，問一問。<br />\n八級只係攞merit，唔高&hellip;重要考試個阿sir比分鬆手先得&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n自己練下d 考試歌當玩下， 覺得ok 咪考埋佢， 反正又唔趕。 考左你講個名出來都好聽d <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b203858b9a3f47c90615065479ef60c22f57ad84","tid":175661,"uid":96732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:41:49.000Z","msg":"學咗3個月鼓 準備考五級試水溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cfb27e1ce6f96486da2dbd21b7342c76ea7b6a","tid":175661,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學咗3個月鼓 準備考五級試水溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一定好勤力練<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3ca37c8dbbd4bc4581f1697e1b3682221bca52","tid":175661,"uid":96732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學咗3個月鼓 準備考五級試水溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一定好勤力練<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n練到唔返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望有回報"},{"pid":"3add68393d7d0c196aac0c918b187df7c1eeaa14","tid":175661,"uid":56837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:38:15.000Z","msg":"最慘係琴行冇演奏級都唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時間想學大提琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9064a4c24f1e61cbdf780e8e1ba1c9d84f764feb","tid":175661,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最慘係琴行冇演奏級都唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時間想學大提琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大提琴正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學過一年"},{"pid":"ee954855611405ea3aa96782fe5f755574373a70","tid":175661,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:00:58.000Z","msg":"古箏, 學左3年半, 本黎今年考8級, on99 唔記得報樂理而家要等明年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 成廿幾歲先學, 應該考埋九級就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<br />\n好想學二胡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實大提琴我都想學, 但要自己帶琴去上堂好 On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49564ea74c428509c018086241a5d39a1beb9c35","tid":175661,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:03:25.000Z","msg":"考左7級琴就考唔到上去，而家諗緊好唔好再take多次8級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d41ab013ce240195a3bfabf456c8aebd76a685","tid":175661,"uid":44420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:05:29.000Z","msg":"violin 8級 黎緊讀music想考埋AT<br />\n好想練琴但係呢排忙到痴線 只係得教琴果陣有少少時間拉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c475ca353b1b10406a4ac6f5ee3d3f585f8a28ff","tid":175661,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:06:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古箏, 學左3年半, 本黎今年考8級, on99 唔記得報樂理而家要等明年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 成廿幾歲先學, 應該考埋九級就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<br />\n好想學二胡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實大提琴我都想學, 但要自己帶琴去上堂好 On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n玩呢d 咁特別樂器， 不如多d 拍片出街玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n收埋收埋好浪費"},{"pid":"1c2e82991f9c2a60f843d18ead96b958e966464f","tid":175661,"uid":44420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古箏, 學左3年半, 本黎今年考8級, on99 唔記得報樂理而家要等明年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 成廿幾歲先學, 應該考埋九級就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<br />\n好想學二胡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bangh