ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 成廿幾歲先學, 應該考埋九級就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<br />\n好想學二胡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實大提琴我都想學, 但要自己帶琴去上堂好 On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大提琴既聲都好正 但係諗起拎咁大隻琴走黎走去好唔方便</blockquote><br />\n電大提琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n方便同多d 玩法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我既諗法係學左傳統先再玩電子rock少少"},{"pid":"740503a44e59cdf276a4ba540f35159e96cda9b5","tid":175661,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:11:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>古箏, 學左3年半, 本黎今年考8級, on99 唔記得報樂理而家要等明年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 成廿幾歲先學, 應該考埋九級就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<br />\n好想學二胡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實大提琴我都想學, 但要自己帶琴去上堂好 On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大提琴既聲都好正 但係諗起拎咁大隻琴走黎走去好唔方便</blockquote><br />\n係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年走入琴行係想報大提琴, 佢一句要自己帶琴我就直接話 &ldquo;咁都係報古箏啦&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個職員都呆左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7861a427d3c9738b2123fc406b2ccde3210086ab","tid":175661,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>古箏, 學左3年半, 本黎今年考8級, on99 唔記得報樂理而家要等明年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 成廿幾歲先學, 應該考埋九級就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<br />\n好想學二胡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實大提琴我都想學, 但要自己帶琴去上堂好 On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大提琴既聲都好正 但係諗起拎咁大隻琴走黎走去好唔方便</blockquote><br />\n係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年走入琴行係想報大提琴, 佢一句要自己帶琴我就直接話 &ldquo;咁都係報古箏啦&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個職員都呆左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前學大提琴， 咩部琴去上堂。 次次搭地鐵都頂到道門同條柱， 攪到斷左頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n之後去左學豎琴"}]}